Data base overview -

What are databases ?
Data bases are systems that allows users to store and organize data
They are useful while dealing with large amounts of data

Data bases uses -
- Data integrity - u can't click on data cell and edit the data like in spreadsheets
- handles massive amount of data
- Quickly combine different datasets
- Automate steps for re-use
- can support data for website and applications

SQL is the programming language used to communicate with the database
